description:
The point shapefile shows number of aircraft handled by each airport in Europe. It also includes the ranking for each airport and percent change in aircraft over 2006. 
Look elswhere on Finder! data related to air traffic, passengers, cargo (both frieght and mail) for major European airports. Use key words: Air traffic, Air travel, Europe
